Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:12.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H94&\an8\3c&HFF00FF&}字幕由ACG12小站，_沉默似金制作，仅供学习交流使用，不得用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.35,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,快治疗满木
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽 快点
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 林
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经用不了魔法了
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.52,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.58,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,满木
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.45,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,满木
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 快逃
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.62,0:00:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我怎么能做出这种事
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.59,0:00:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我不走 不能抛下你不管
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.59,0:00:46.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,拜托了 林
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大家
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫你们快走啊
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.47,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.76,0:00:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.39,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,满木
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.52,0:01:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.23,0:01:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.28,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从哪里 怎样回到地面上的 我已经不记得了
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.50,0:01:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是身体记住了路了吧
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.71,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被筱原先生捡到加入了奥利安
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.55,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但是梅丽很快就离开了
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.76,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我在他眼前 让他很难受
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.39,0:01:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她虽然什么都没说 但她的眼神这么诉说道
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.97,0:01:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看到我就会回想起无法挽回的过去
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.15,0:01:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不看
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这让她很难受
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.78,0:01:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,之后梅丽辗转加入了许多队伍 但全都没有长驻
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.74,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,传到我耳中的评价也和我所知到的她完全不一样
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.79,0:02:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实把梅丽带回了地面上
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.05,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的她是一具空壳
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.30,0:02:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,她的心可能仍旧留在那个地方
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她拜托你们了
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不 请别这样
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,失去同伴的痛苦 我也非常清楚
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有过这样的经验
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要忘记现在心痛的感觉
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.29,0:02:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,即使怀着痛苦 你们也能继续前进
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.29,0:02:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜现在的同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.59,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴都是失去了就再也回不来的人
Dialogue: 100,0:02:56.09,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,并且基本上 都是在失去后才会察觉到这一点
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,听了很没劲的事
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么很没劲啊
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.32,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人的情况我是知道了
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那又怎么样
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟我们没有直接关系吧
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,话是这么说...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有着沉重的过去所以我们要温柔对待她？
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我没这么说
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.80,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是在这么说 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那女人跟我们有什么不一样吗
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就不难受吗
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我们的错吗
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.73,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不把握门当同伴的家伙 为什么我一定要承认他是同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露？
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.95,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多...不在了以后
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.83,0:05:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没有...不难过得人吧
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很难过
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.13,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我希望大家能同时也温柔起来
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是我们
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.14,0:05:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还是梅丽小姐 尽量...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.52,0:05:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽跟我们没什么不一样 你是这么说的吧 蓝德
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,说了又怎么样
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.82,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 我们没有试图去理解梅丽
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那么梅丽也没办法理解我们不是吗
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.24,0:06:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不觉得梅丽是同伴 那么梅丽也不会觉得我们是同伴 不是吗
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.96,0:06:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你有试图理解我吗 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.34,0:06:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我怎么想 有什么意见 你们总是一直无视我好吗
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.97,0:06:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为蓝德总是说多余的话
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.94,0:06:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 因为你只会说多余的话
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.11,0:06:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.36,0:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿被说平胸也会很受伤
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这种就叫做多余的话
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索？
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.95,0:06:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我都没发现
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有注意观察的 不只是梅丽一个人
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.42,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 蓝德
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今后我会注意的
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为蓝德是我的同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什...什么？
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那就自己注意点啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这就叫多余
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,叫笨蛋笨蛋有什么不好的 笨蛋
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,烦死了 让我也想想
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想想？蓝德你？
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.12,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是要想明天该怎么面对那女人
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.16,0:07:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那啥 席赫露
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没想让你那么说的
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是不是要下雨了
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很多余啊
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.72,0:07:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了 可能会下雪哦
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 应该这么说
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.93,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.23,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 明天应该怎么面对梅丽好呢 我们
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的下雨了啊
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 哈尔
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我在想下雨了
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔 那把短刀...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.30,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我掉的刀
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 梦儿
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉我今天状态有点怪
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没事了
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跟踪它吧
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定能找到他们的老巢
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.26,0:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没找到适合的哥布林
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回去吧 这么大的雨
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 梅丽 我有话想跟你说
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在？
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快点说完
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我话说在前面
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想让我退队的话就直说好了
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 梅丽 不是这样的
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.71,0:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起来 今天我们有点怪
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.21,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为昨天听了那种事 不知道该如何跟梅丽接触
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.35,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么跟她说话
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.93,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽感到不对劲看 全神戒备 看上去似乎预感到了什么
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,例如告别 结束
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.07,0:10:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽 我有事项告诉你
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.62,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的队伍以前是有神官的
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.66,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫马纳多
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.22,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的队伍以前是有神官的
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫马纳多
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多死了
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.35,0:10:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说是为我们才死的
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.19,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们受伤 哪怕是擦伤 马纳多也会马上治好
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他还和莫古索两个人一起当前卫
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.08,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是我们的队长 一个人负责了三个职位
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他是个很厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知何时 这样变得理所当然了起来
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想马纳多应该也不轻松
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.55,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是没有表现出来
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.10,0:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全没有想象过马纳多的心情
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也只能想象了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.11,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为马纳多死了 已经不在了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.24,0:11:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多不在了以后 说实话我觉得已经不行了
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.41,0:11:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只要还活着 就不能什么都不做
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们邀请了梅丽
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有神官什么都干不成
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因为这个理由 没有什么别的了
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是呢 我们本来也都是被剩下的
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是马纳多把我们集合都了一起 才成了一支队伍
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,成为了伙伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.52,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我们成为了伙伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在一支队伍里 也会有不顺利的事
Dialogue: 100,0:12:21.70,0:12:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也会有火大的情况 也会有吵架的时候
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.70,0:12:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可是大家还是彼此重要的同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,比起为什么成为了同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是同伴这一点更重要
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我认为 梅丽也是同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我...我也是 认为你是同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.64,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 梅丽很可爱
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我...有梅丽小姐在就很安心
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.94,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也那啥 稍微受点小伤就大惊小怪的 也不是没在反省啦
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多算是同伴了吧？
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.83,0:13:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会下雪了啊
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,蓝德居然在反省
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这梗能别玩了吗
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.44,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽 那个 如果不介意的话 要不要一起去买 莫古索的头盔
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.29,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 这个也是不介意的话 一起吃个晚饭吧
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.88,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 还不能...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能？
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 明天见
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.32,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 只要还活着 新的明天就会到来
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 能找到可爱的头盔
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,钱也总算凑够了
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然蓝德1铜都没出
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.84,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,砍价砍掉的部分都算我出的 白痴
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.84,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索的头盔 靠蓝德强行砍价
Dialogue: 100,0:14:48.51,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,从45银居然砍到了18银
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.93,0:15:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟梅丽的距离 应该 也在一点点 一点点缩短了
Dialogue: 100,0:15:44.28,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一天一次 我们一定会去那个地方
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哥布林杀手
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,最近如何啊 哥布林杀手
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也要去达姆洛吗 哥布林杀手
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.43,0:16:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙总有一天会把哥布林全杀光的吧
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了 可恶
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别理他们 反正也没说错
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝 这碗汤
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.85,0:16:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要不要也烧烧看
Dialogue: 100,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意是类似品的话
Dialogue: 100,0:16:31.03,0:16:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每天 每天 都是哥布林 哥布林 哥布林 哥布林
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.16,0:16:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是晴天还是雨天 都是哥布林哥布林哥布林哥布林哥布林哥布林...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始觉得每只都长得差不多
Dialogue: 100,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最近能开始分清差别了
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雄多雌少
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听梅丽说
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.60,0:17:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分雄性都在达姆洛新街区 被阶级高的雄性在给簇拥着
Dialogue: 100,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不羡慕这种后宫啊
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.11,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,雌哥布林应该也不喜欢蓝德这样的类型
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.99,0:17:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是不明白我的魅力的笨蛋脑子有问题
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明白的人一下子就会明白的
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.91,0:17:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,例如梅丽 要从我们三个男人里选谁你选谁
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不用害羞哦
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我害羞什么
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.19,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哟哟哟 怎么样 杀得好吗
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.69,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,确实没看到过呢 梅丽笑的样子
Dialogue: 100,0:17:59.87,0:18:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭要吃有营养的东西
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,住在破破的义勇兵宿舍就行了
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,与其把钱用在住好的旅馆 现在更需要买装备
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.80,0:18:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是要先把莫古索的防具武装起来
Dialogue: 100,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,全套的金属板甲我们肯定买不起
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.80,0:18:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,找到价钱合适的二手 就去找盔甲锻制师修改尺寸
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是这样 一个部位还是要好几十银
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是技能
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.32,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我学了消除脚步声的潜行和猛击
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,席赫露的催眠暗影 是让敌人沉睡的影魔法
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exhaust
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是瞬间与敌人拉开距离的技能
Dialogue: 100,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.33,0:18:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,把技能名全部喊出声只是蓝德的爱好
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莫古索的呐喊能够使敌人僵直一瞬
Dialogue: 100,0:18:59.01,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,梦儿学会了鹰眼 提升弓箭的命中率
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.77,0:19:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,穴鼠技能能够飞快回避敌人的攻击
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.69,0:19:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,梅丽原本便是比我们高好几级的神官
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.95,0:19:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让人很安心 很少见的 我也不知道为什么 会觉得应该砍那里
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.29,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,刀能够轻易刺入 刀尖碰到了什么东西的时候
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会觉得就是这里
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在我这么想的时候 已经贯穿了它
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.55,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这道光是什么 其实我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 100,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,下次问问看芭芭拉老师吧
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.31,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了吧 哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 差不多吧
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去郊游的前一天晚上会睡不着之类的？
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 100,0:20:34.94,0:20:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多 不用担心 我没有逞强
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.20,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.00,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.88,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来到格林姆加尔之后 过了多少天来着
Dialogue: 100,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何时 我开始不再数数了
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事是确凿无疑的
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.07,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我们是从哪里来的 我们现在都是同伴
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,确实都一起存活在这里
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.50,0:21:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在的样子 真想也让你看看
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,马纳多
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:33.92,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur0.5\c&H141621&}[Episode 7]\N{\fs70}被称为哥布林杀手
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.00,0:23:37.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.4\c&H141621&}[Episode 8]\N{\fs70}为了与你的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:37.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur8\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\alpha&H30&}[Episode 8]\N{\fs70}为了与你的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:57.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Road of dust Beyond here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.71,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Out beyond that dirt road…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:08.80,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The black horses trample forth across the dry lands
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.89,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Out beyond the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:18.22,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The soaring hawks peer out through to the gusty wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:22.56,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And the harsh winds howl on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:27.44,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The desert wolves cry on too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:33.11,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And here, lies the bleak and dry dusty crossroads
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:37.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}One path shows us what we must do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.66,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So take my hand and let's go on through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.42,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the barren desert lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where the harshest heat scorches the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.96,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And so lets go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.76,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}please ride with me on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.76,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the dusty arid lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:16:01.68,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where the scorches of the sun goes on... and on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:33.34,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As the sun dies down, the land sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H00F200&}(The moon sits high above the sky)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:36.30,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They sleep(It shines bright)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Until the break of dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.93,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}As earth's servants sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Under desert stars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8\3c&H00F200&}(The stars look down on the land)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.48,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They sleep(It shines bright)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:48.15,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Until the sun rises up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:03.04,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Out beyond that dirt road…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:08.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wild horse we ride along past with our motor bikes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:13.01,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Out beyond that desert
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:18.43,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where that rusty station once stood is now nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:22.60,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And the harsh heat scorches on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:27.77,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The dry dusty earth burns too
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:33.03,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And here, lies the bleak and dry arid crossroads
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:37.57,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That path shows us what we must do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.66,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So take my hand and let's ride on through
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:44.50,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the barren desert lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.96,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where the harshest heat scorches the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:48.87,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And so lets go
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.75,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}please ride with me on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.59,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the dusty arid lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:18:02.14,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where the scorches of the sun goes on... and on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:28.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is this where we stand right here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:33.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}On... this road
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:38.17,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shall we ride out this path now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:41.22,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So take my hand and let's ride on through
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the barren desert lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.43,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where scent of burnt engine oil lingers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And shall we go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.44,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}please ride with me on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:55.11,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the dusty arid lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:59.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where the horses run on around wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.33,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now take my hand and let's fight on through
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.17,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the barren desert lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.76,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where our headlights shine out on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.80,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now we must go
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}please trust me now on
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.05,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the dusty arid lands of mother earth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:30.81,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Out to the horizon out on that path we ride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:58.67,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dusty roads Beyond here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.91,0:03:11.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,擦り傷だらけの昨日を繰り返して
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.66,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,僕らは拓く希望の明日を
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.14,0:03:34.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,このちっぽけな両手に何が残ってるだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.64,0:03:40.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,仰いだ声は空へ散っていった
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,手に入れた現実は燻んでて
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,目の前が見えなくなっても
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.69,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,一緒なら長く続くこの道を
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.16,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,進んで行ける
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.61,0:04:00.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,埃にまみれた絆を繋いでく
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.01,0:04:06.75,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,過去と未来背中合わせの僕らは
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.38,0:04:13.93,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,間違いだらけの答えを繰り返して
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.93,0:04:19.18,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,光を求め手を伸ばすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.97,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,何度だって
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.91,0:03:11.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,遍体鳞伤的昨日 循环上演
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.66,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,我们要开拓 希望的明天
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.14,0:03:34.64,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,在这双空无一物的手中 还残留下些什么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.64,0:03:40.52,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,抬头仰望声音消散于天空
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.02,0:03:44.23,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,得到的现实熏得焦黑
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.40,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,即使看不清前方
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.40,0:03:50.69,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,大家一起便能大步前进
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.16,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,走在这条漫长的道路上
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.61,0:04:00.54,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,串联起满是尘埃的羁绊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.01,0:04:06.75,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,过去与未来 我们背靠背
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.38,0:04:13.93,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,重复着错误不断的答案
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.93,0:04:19.18,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,渴求着光芒伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:21.97,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,无论多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:13.32,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,つめたい雨上がりの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:19.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,渇いた空気ふれてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:26.05,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,芽生える花のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:32.31,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,想いのかけら溢れてくるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:44.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,この手に貰えた君のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:54.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,宝物になる未来へ導いてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:03.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,ずっと君の声を追いかけていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:09.44,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,いつからなんだろう強くなったね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:16.53,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,広い世界探したものは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:24.24,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,旅路の果てにきっと見つかるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:13.32,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,冰冷的雨停后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:19.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,试着触碰干渴的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:26.05,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,如同冒芽的花一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:32.31,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,感情的碎片 满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:44.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,手中得到的 你的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:54.00,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,成为宝物 将我引导向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:23:03.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,一直 追赶着你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:09.44,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,是从何时开始的呢 变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:16.53,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,彷徨在这浩淼的世界 我始终坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:24.24,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,在旅途尽头 一定能找到 我所探寻之物
